devdoc.details: All functions are called by the SaveDoc contract

convertTypeDoc(address,uint8,uint8,uint2.details: Change type of document (create a copy and delete the old one)

params.ownerCopyNFT: owner of the copy of the document

delAllCopyDoc(address).details: Delete all copy, certified and pending transfered documents

delCopyDoc(address,uint8,uint256).details: Delete copy of secured document according owner, type and index

getAllCopyPendingTransfer(address).details: Get all secured documents in pending transfer state

returns._0: all secured documents in pending transfer state

getAllCopyShared(address).details: Get all copies of secured documents

getIndexNFT(address,uint8,uint256).details: Get index of document according to owner, type and tokenID

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
